{"tid":2217710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球金融中心最行排名　上海已超越香港","createTime":"2020-09-25T15:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T15:20:58.000Z","uid":225931,"like":698,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"e6de724abac2863ed5e22fe741525662c0195523","tid":2217710,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"9月25日，由中國（深圳）綜合開發研究院和英國智庫 Z/Yen 集團聯合編制的「第28期全球金融中心指數（GFCI 28）」報吿正式發佈。最新報吿排名顯示，全球前十大金融中心排名依次為：紐約、倫敦、上海、東京、香港、新加坡、北京、舊金山、深圳、蘇黎世。<br />\n<br />\n在全球五大金融中心中，上海正在連續追趕超越。與第27期全球金融中心排名相比，本期全球十大金融中心排名順序發生較大變化。其中，上海評分再次上升，超過東京首次進入全球三強行列，代表了中國城市在全球金融中心的最高地位。<br />\n<br />\n在最近的三期排名中，上海連升三級。在去年9月發佈的第26期「全球金融中心指數」排名，上海還處於第五位，今年3月，上海上升到第四位，這次首次進入全球三強。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4c2e0bcbf18170c8351e3887267a8000f4e8a6","tid":2217710,"uid":237459,"like":41,"dislike":36,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"已經輸咗了"},{"pid":"8b284a00cf29b91a3e9357ab52b1130269c02847","tid":2217710,"uid":286897,"like":340,"dislike":3,"score":337,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8556c064351a78da16edc4f787ff83387c2d9ec","tid":2217710,"uid":63670,"like":499,"dislike":2,"score":497,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"都好正常啊<br />\n賣出買入都可以話操縱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要俾毒品調查科搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁'自由'"},{"pid":"8d13cd7b050b352fde7661b828f297b1d6ca80bf","tid":2217710,"uid":191926,"like":301,"dislike":1,"score":300,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"香港已經嚴重強國化<br />\n<br />\n就好像倫交所串鳩香港<br />\n<br />\n同香港 不如直接同上海合作"},{"pid":"1a1ad6786a4402b24094873b92a8326f833a52e7","tid":2217710,"uid":194298,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"好啦美國唔怕取消所有香港地位喇，因為咱們有上海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59eafe6063122b56de02f17c15b0d0ddd333e3d","tid":2217710,"uid":36128,"like":154,"dislike":2,"score":152,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"上海強大了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱愛中國既香港人仲唔快D移民過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b44c03bf788624830c2a48c0d85076932d6bc7a","tid":2217710,"uid":370061,"like":8,"dislike":67,"score":-59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"上海超越香港都勉強可信（數量非質量）你話上海超新加坡真係笑大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235ded19e850b6b73452d961577eef43fc934498","tid":2217710,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"政府：香港金融中心指數排名上升<br />\n英國Z/Yen集團與中國（深圳）綜合開發研究院聯合發布新一期《全球金融中心指數》報告，香港總排名全球第五位。政府表示，香港是五大領先金融中心之一，是次排名較3月報告的排名上升一位。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n政府指，報告中總排名第三至第七位金融中心的整體評分非常接近，在以數據為依歸的五類競爭力領域，即營商環境、人力資本、基礎設施、金融業發展水平和聲譽，香港排名均為首五位，而營商環境和人力資本更位列第三。與兩個總排名較高的金融中心比較，香港在四類競爭力的排名均較高。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n報告指出，在持續不確定的國際貿易情況、2019冠狀病毒病疫情影響和地緣政治的大環境下，所有金融中心得分平均數顯著下降，香港整體評分和排名則比3月上升。政府表示，在疫情影響下，全球面對不同程度挑戰，香港金融體系仍堅韌穩健，金融服務業各環節運作有序，聯繫匯率一如既往運作良好。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n此外，香港擁有國際金融中心的制度優勢，基礎實力強勁，監管制度有效透明、與國際標準一致，並且擁有大量金融人才和產品，這些競爭優勢將維持香港作為全球領先金融中心地位。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n香港是國際及中資企業首選上巿集資平台，去年和今年續有大型新經濟企業選擇在香港作主要或第二上市。香港是全球最大離岸人民幣業務中心，也是亞洲第二大私募基金管理中心。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n政府表示，香港在「一國兩制」下會繼續發揮金融體系獨特優勢，當局會加大力度推廣香港作為全球領先金融中心及通往中國內地和國際市場的雙向門戶，並抓緊粵港澳大灣區和「一帶一路」倡議的龐大機遇，進一步加強香港作為資產和財富管理中心、離岸人民幣業務中心、保險和風險管理中心及綠色和可持續金融樞紐地位，同時促進金融科技發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/09/20200925/20200925_183725_732.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F09%2F20200925%2F20200925_183725_732.html&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=4db79d23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/09/20200925/20200925_183725_732.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1a5e21aebe2d1207ea4bf520ab381df3515e76","tid":2217710,"uid":60545,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"不如話已超越紐約<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd91994bae8007ed37b4cdd20bf60153f5bfb258","tid":2217710,"uid":57023,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"quote":{"pid":"9b1a5e21aebe2d1207ea4bf520ab381df3515e76","tid":2217710,"uid":60545,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"不如話已超越紐約<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T18:42:48.000Z","msg":"反正都係深圳搞既排名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在國際財經領域上有乜公信力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20046e7d85ea19331aa07efb9e1295b1391aab63","tid":2217710,"uid":188282,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T18:56:45.000Z","msg":"由中國（深圳）綜合開發研究院&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"f9cd2c275810775232f06bf4f8416cbaa15437fe","tid":2217710,"uid":30040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T22:25:22.000Z","msg":"以後挘水係咪搵上海挘先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2494fc1db2d8c3f2189ee5f402ca6293f74bead9","tid":2217710,"uid":289191,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T22:43:42.000Z","msg":"偉大的黨終於為中国人一雪前恥<br />\n英國人湊大的孽種XG<br />\n終於不敵自家乖仔SH"},{"pid":"8617711fe9360f0398935abad0128e929e40ab5b","tid":2217710,"uid":104804,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:03:09.000Z","msg":"最好全中國都超越香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a21456c926df87c03436993fbc7969e2c754440","tid":2217710,"uid":204309,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6b44c03bf788624830c2a48c0d85076932d6bc7a","tid":2217710,"uid":370061,"like":8,"dislike":67,"score":-59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"上海超越香港都勉強可信（數量非質量）你話上海超新加坡真係笑大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:07:35.000Z","msg":"雖然成日同新加坡比<br />\n但新加坡其實唔入流架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個會想去果邊開間公司"},{"pid":"38b80a3a10fcc0ae7dd29ed2882fd4c6a6406430","tid":2217710,"uid":166729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:08:51.000Z","msg":"又超越<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 集唔集到資呀？"},{"pid":"6d871e1e132c661cec690b29fbd64dcf199a6214","tid":2217710,"uid":52146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:09:18.000Z","msg":"香港將出現回流潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055c20009c1517f00d8b0473b99f9d151c398e57","tid":2217710,"uid":245347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:11:19.000Z","msg":"準備好超英趕美了！！！！！"},{"pid":"64a8e0bb06988f750d3a5a4ba5c11a924a36f28e","tid":2217710,"uid":275218,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:14:35.000Z","msg":"英國Z/Yen集團與中國（深圳）綜合開發研究院聯合<br />\n我呀媽夠話我靚仔啦"},{"pid":"6f70e0660877c8b105aa7b2332fb83b95df3bfe9","tid":2217710,"uid":69614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:18:00.000Z","msg":"推逃犯條例就係為咗搞衰香港讓上海取代<br />\n喺鬥爭文化下 香港點都唔會政治正確<br />\n<br />\n不過現階段都只係喺深圳研究上取代到"},{"pid":"993263d69622e4dd355b47772b3d0912b1a99f51","tid":2217710,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"h